replies.content: You are at the forum of the ducks of course!
You definitely shouldn't call the police. Just hide the body in the forest and run to Cuba
No matter what, The Duck is always rigth, apologize immediately!
I once met a guy, who knew a guy whose sister in law had a rubber duck farm. You can call them.
